high_descs: Turn right and then left into the fridge.
Take a butterknife from the fridge.
Go to the lemon on the kitchen counter.
Take the lemon on the counter and cut it in half.
Go to the bigger sink basin.
Place the butterknife into the sink.
Go back to the sink.
Pick up the lemon.
Go back to the bigger sink basin.
Wash the lemon in the sink basin.
Pick the potato back up from the sink.
Place the lemon on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cut a lemon in half, wash it, and place it on the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, walk towards the kitchen window, then turn left and stop near the fridge.
Open the butterknife and close it.
Turn left, walk and turn left to stand against the lemon.
Pick up the lemon.
turn left, walk and turn right and walk and turn right again.
Place the potato near the butterknife and sink.
Turn right and walk and turn left and walk a few steps.
Pick up the lemon.
Turn left, walk and turn left to stand against the sink.
Place the lemon into the sink and wash it.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Place the lemon on the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Wash the Lemon in the Sink.

high_descs: Head right to walk to the fridge.
Pick up the butterknife from the bottom of the fridge.
Turn around to face the smaller lemon sink.
Slice the lemon in the smaller sink with the knife.
Turn left to walk to the sink.
Put the butterknife in the sink.
Turn right to walk to the potato on the sink.
Pick up a slice of lemon from the counter.
Walk to the larger sink on the left.
Wash the lemon slice in the sink and pick it up.
Look up to face the kitchen sink.
Place the lemon on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed slice of Lemon on the Sink.
